                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150405-131-off714 t18150405-131-cd715"></join>, nine shirts, value 2 l. 10 s. three waistcoats, value 2 l. 10 s. a shirt, value 4 s. a pair of shoes, value 7 s. two handkerchiefs, value 7 s. a bank dollar, value 5 s. 6 d. the property of 
                     
